<p dir=3D"auto"><em>Robby's theme is the default one. It's not the fanciest=
 one. It's not the simplest one. It's just the right one (for him).</em></p=
>
<p dir=3D"auto">Once you find a theme that you'd like to use, you will need=
 to edit the <code>~/.zshrc</code> file. You'll see an environment variable=
 (all caps) in there that looks like:</p>
<div class=3D"highlight highlight-source-shell notranslate position-relativ=
