0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"></path></svg></a>Custom Plugins And T=
hemes</h3>
<p dir=3D"auto">If you want to override any of the default behaviors, just =
add a new file (ending in <code>.zsh</code>) in the <code>custom/</code> di=
rectory.</p>
<p dir=3D"auto">If you have many functions that go well together, you can p=
ut them as a <code>XYZ.plugin.zsh</code> file in the <code>custom/plugins/<=
/code> directory and then enable this plugin.</p>
<p dir=3D"auto">If you would like to override the functionality of a plugin=
 distributed with Oh My Zsh, create a plugin of the same name in the <code>=
custom/plugins/</code> directory and it will be loaded instead of the one i=
n <code>plugins/</code>.</p>
